src:
I denne trønderkommunen tjener de minst
05 Nov 2019, 10:33 by Alexander Killingberg,Espen Rasmussen
Verran er trønderkommunen hvor innbyggerne i snitt tjener minst.
Det viser skattelistene for inntektsåret 2018 som ble tilgjengelig tirsdag.
text:
In this Trondheim municipality they earn the least
05 Nov 2019, 10:33 by Alexander Killingberg, Espen Rasmussen
Verran is the municipality of Trøndel where the average population earns the least.
It shows the tax lists for the 2018 fiscal year that became available Tuesday.
